+1 on this, I've run into this today after trying --turbo again in Next. Because I have one alias for Panda's generated styles, I'll either have to figure out how to make the alias work or move my files (or just wait until the next release to try --turbo lol)

```js
experimental: {
    turbo: {
      resolveAlias: {
        "@/styled-system/*": "styled-system/*",
      },
    },
  },
```

The [docs here](https://turbo.build/pack/docs/features/customizing-turbopack#resolve-aliases) imply this may work due to the reference to "similar to webpack's [resolve.alias](https://webpack.js.org/configuration/resolve/#resolvealias)"

